Dr. Mungai clearly cares about the subject, but I found her disorganized and unclear in her instructions. Worse, she was unapproachable outside of class, and in class seemed to rush to judgment and become offended by critical discussion (ironic in a class about cultural understanding.) You'd probably be better served to just sit quietly and listen.

Dr. Mundai is the best professor at Adelphi University. She has her students' interest at heart. She is very helpful and accommodating. Students Don't miss her classes. Sign up . You will not be sorry. Keep up the good work Dr.Mungai.
